    If you'd like to become an educator for your state, apply
    <a class="wax-apply-link" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfcNuR8NCVqdo-3wZD4PuTUsR90-CWazq8ahe7Am6nGLcZ_xw/viewform?usp=sharing&ouid=107461442807732303611" target="_blank">here</a>.
  </p>
</div>
